reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing. I feel so safe!
reviews.reviewText: This little gadget is incredible, especially for the price! My husband has to go out of town on buisness trips. We just moved into a new apartment complex and although I feel relatively safe, I'm an idiot and listen to a lot of true crime podcasts. Lol. Plus our door only has one lock and it just made me uneasy. Once you get the hang of how to use this item, which honestly took me once or twice to get, it's so easy. It will keep your door shut even if it's unlocked. I highly recommend this. I might even give it as stocking stuffers this year for Christmas.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I used to use a jimmy stick under my door knob at home. This works great. It took me a few times to get used to how it works now I am a pro at it. I really feel safe.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Unusual little gadget
reviews.reviewText: Took a quick minute to figure out how to install. Sent with daughter overseas and not sure if she'll use it. But the concept is solid, so if I ever need one, I'd use it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I was skeptical but this passed the test! People were always barging in my office and my request for a lock to be installed is still "pending". In the meantime, this keeps unwanted visitors at bay and is fully and easily removable. I now have one in use at home and keep the other in my bag for a quick and easy barricade to use at any time. I highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought it for my stay in a hotel and it’s legit! It keeps the door secured even when it’s unlocked and you try to open it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Doesn’t fit some doors
reviews.reviewText: I knew there was a chance that it would not fit in some locks, but I purchased it for an airbnb trip and it was not even close to fitting. I’m sure this would help add an extra layer of security for many, but if I could go back I would’ve ordered a door boot instead.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A MUST HAVE to feel safe while traveling
reviews.reviewText: This is a must have, especially for those who travel and stay in motels/hotels. It's easy to use, provides protection. It's perfect! Great stocking stuffer too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great product for feeling safer while traveling
reviews.reviewText: A word of advice, practice using these on various doors and locks before taking them on a trip. I tried them once and then used them on trip. I almost sent them back. Practice. Once you get it down how they work and go on, it is a great product. I always feel a little nervous in hotel rooms and VRBO rentals where other people may have a key to get in & this product makes me feel safer while away from home.
